728188f-a.title: Queens: Welling Court - 30th Avenue
728188f-a.text:
(1) 29 Welling Court (old number), north side, west of 30th Ave. (right not shown.) The white house was about a century old when Roe H. Smith purchased it. One Allen was the owner in 1934. Roe H. Smith occupied it in 1840.

1922

Eugene  L. Armbruster Collection

(2) The same, another view.

1922

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection

728189f-a.title: Queens: Welling Court - 30th Avenue
728189f-a.text:
(1)
1145 Welling Court (also 15 Welling Street or St. George Place;) north side, west of Thirtieth Ave. (right), showing the Furman house. Fred Trowbridge was also an occupant or owner.
